{"tid":203830,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下邊到仲有apotop d ram賣","createTime":"2017-04-16T14:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T03:31:04.000Z","uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6185ec6ace625e05a22c1699833aadd9e72bdd8","tid":203830,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"請教咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  渣住1條apotop ddr3 8gb ram 宜家想加多條<br />\n但行過黃金 都無鋪頭賣"},{"pid":"8f963ff779941e1687641c3521bd2f46f401421b","tid":203830,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請教咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  渣住1條apotop ddr3 8gb ram 宜家想加多條<br />\n但行過黃金 都無鋪頭賣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要同頻率同latency就可以，唔一定要同牌子<br />\n<br />\n唔知就用cpu-z睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/L2MB5m9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FL2MB5m9.jpg&h=06d10f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用我自己做例子就係3200Mhz(個1600要x2)<br />\nlatency就係14(CL)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c944afac49ba28c11ab72f52f6306d7384d31f4e","tid":203830,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T18:03:26.000Z","msg":"學到野 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/plk0s39c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fplk0s39c&h=4028c550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢個情怳係咪買普通 DDR3  1600MHz 就ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"eae7200e72746fb7670613bf109d3a8116e4dc27","tid":203830,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學到野 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/plk0s39c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fplk0s39c&h=4028c550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢個情怳係咪買普通 DDR3  1600MHz 就ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你依加用緊係 1600 11-11-12-28 最理想係可以對返呢幾隻數字。<br />\n<br />\n驟眼搵比較接近既<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/17/031538_770b34a1f74b668a984cfa4c4490db58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F17%2F031538_770b34a1f74b668a984cfa4c4490db58.jpg&h=d98ba908&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9z2bL9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9z2bL9p.jpg&h=8a7b92db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩款都係 1600 11-11-11-28<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就睇埋電壓，比如上邊兩隻都係1.5V@1600<br />\n假如你底板每個Ram位可以獨立改電壓就無乜所謂，如果唔得就要揀一樣電壓。<br />\n<br />\n最後就比較少人理既位，就係Ram上邊有唔同放晶片既方法，有單邊雙邊。道理同上，理想就單對單<br />\n、雙對雙。實際上有無影響我唔清楚，可能要交比專業既巴打答<br />\n<br />\n以上所有野係集我自己所識，去馬之前請自己再google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錯請指出"},{"pid":"875f510f5d901caad2ba145fae4a2dfde437acec","tid":203830,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂"}]}